('Edge computing: dynamic and sustainable provisioning of mobile services', 10, 'fabianachiasserini.carla@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['giaccone.paolo@tmtest.polito.it']::text[], ARRAY['DOCKER','EDGE COMPUTING']::text[], 'EXPERIMENTAL AND MODELING', ARRAY['Telecommunication Networks Group']::text[], 'The adoption of Virtual Function Virtualization (VNF) in 5G networks enables an unprecedented level of flexibility in providing new network services, but this comes at the cost of orchestrating carefully the required resources (cpu, memory, storage, network).
