('Improve robustness of FPGA dataflow accelerators for Convolutional Neural Networks', 487, 'passerone.claudio@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['Pierpaolo Morì']::text[], ARRAY['CNNS','FPGA','HLS','HW','ROBUSTNESS','TRAINING']::text[], 'RICERCA', ARRAY['L-21 group 2']::text[], 'The aim of this thesis is to demonstrate the effectiveness of Fault Aware Training (FAT) on dataflow FPGA accelerators for CNNs. The work will be organized in two main milestones:
