('Real-Time 3D Object Pose Estimator using AI on Edge', 544, 'lavagno.luciano@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['Marcello Babbi','Reply Torino']::text[], ARRAY['IMAGE ANALYSIS','MACHINE LEARNING']::text[], 'APPLIED RESEARCH', ARRAY['Microelectronics']::text[], 'The accurate and real-time estimation of 3D poses of objects has many practical applications in various
domains, such as robotics, smart agriculture and augmented reality. This thesis proposes the development of
a state-of-the-art 3D pose estimator using AI and deploying it on edge devices. The system will use computer
