('User interface for the generation of general purpose functional tests', 91, 'lamberti.fabrizio@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY['machine that will actually implement/run it',' the ','machine that will actually implement/run it']::text[], 'TESI CON TIROCINIO', ARRAY['Gr-09 - Graphics And Intelligent Systems - Grains']::text[], 'The topic of this thesis proposal falls within the context of a collaboration of the GRAINS research group of the Control and Computer Engineering (DAUIN) Department with CREA - COLLAUDI ELETTRONICI AUTOMATIZZATI S.R.L. in Ciriè (TO). 
 The goal is to create, based on the outcomes of an already completed design phase, a visual environment for the development of functional tests capable to preserve a neat separation between the specification of the test and the machine that will actually implement/run it, thus allowing a given test sequence to be executed on different machines without any rewriting. 
 The subjects presented above could be tackled in ONE OR MORE THESIS WORKS, which will be developed at the company''s premises or in Politecnico di Torino''s research labs. 
 Candidates will be requested to have good programming skills in C/C++ and, optionally, experience with the use of libraries/frameworks/toolkits for creating graphics applications.', ARRAY[]::text[], '', '2024-08-26', 2, ARRAY['LM-13 - Master Degree in Pharmacy and Industrial Pharmacy','LM-32 - Master Degree in Computer Engineering','LM-31 - Master Degree in Management Engineering']::text[]),
('Superfici funzionali avanzate micro e nano-strutturate superidrofobiche e autopulenti', 7, 'lucajanner.davide@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY['LASER','MARCATURA','PROCESSO PRODUTTIVO']::text[], 'I E II LIVELLO', ARRAY['Aa - Glasses','Ceramics And Composites']::text[], 'La tesi si propone di realizzare mediante l''utilizzo di tecniche di microfabbricazione avanzate (film sottili, litografia, laser machining ed etching) la realizzazione di superfici funzionali per applicazioni legate a superfici auto-pulenti e superidrorepellenti. Per le tesi di tesi di II livello è prevista un''attività di tipo sperimentale.', ARRAY['Interazione luce materiali, microfabbricazione']::text[], '', '2024-04-09', 1, ARRAY['L-03 - Visual Arts, Music, Performing Arts, and Fashion','L-06 - Geography']::text[]),
