('Metodologie integrate di Life Cycle Assessment e Life Cycle Cost per lo sviluppo di sistemi aeronautici tramite "circular design"', 358, 'brusa.eugenio@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['Ing. Guido Pavan (Former Leonardo Company)']::text[], ARRAY['CIRCULAR DESIGN','MODELLAZIONE DI SISTEMA','SVILUPPO PRODOTTO','SYSTEMS ENGINEERING']::text[], 'NUMERICA E PROGETTUALE', ARRAY['20-Industrial Systems Engineering And Design']::text[], 'L''applicazione dell''economia circolare alla progettazione meccanica e meccatronica dei sistemi di bordo per velivoli implica una attenta predizione dei consumi e delle risorse impiegate in fase di produzione, esercizio e dismissione che è documentata a progetto sia dal LCA che dal LCC. La tesi opera su un caso test tale integrazione e indirizza all''utilizzo dei metodi indicati.', ARRAY['Fondamenti del corso di ingegneria meccanica o aerospaziale']::text[], '', '2024-10-16', 2, ARRAY['LM-20 - Master Degree in Aerospace and Astronautical Engineering','LM-02 - Master Degree in Archaeology','LM-24 - Master Degree in Building Systems Engineering']::text[]),
('Protecting privacy online with stable diffusion models', 140, 'morra.lia@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY['DEEP LEARNING','IMMAGINI DIGITALI','RETI NEURALI PROFONDE']::text[], 'Tesi di Laurea', ARRAY['Dauin - Gr-09 - Graphics And Intelligent Systems - Grains']::text[], 'Current social media generate a tremendous amount of visual material, that can be exploited by researchers operating in social media research, digital humanities, and marketing. However, privacy regulations impose significant restrictions to both data collection and sharing. The CAMOUFLAGE project, funded by the AI4Media European project, aims to exploit diffusion model (such as Stable Diffusion) to produce a  synthetic version of an existing image, presenting equivalent visual and semantic characteristics of the original, while at the same time fully preserving the anonymity of the user who published the image. The project has a strong multidisciplinary focus and will be carried out in collaboration with researchers in visual semiotics to determine the quality and information content of the generated image. The system will be tested on a collection of real Facebook and Instagram profile pictures. Multiple thesis are available tackling three distinct, yet related, research objectives: to design and implement controllable image synthesis that retains the visual and semantic content of a target image; to determine whether the resulting synthetic images can be considered successfully anonymized, in comparison with state-of-the-art solutions based on GANs; and whether the synthetic collection has the same information content of the original image.', ARRAY['deep learning, pytorch']::text[], '', '2024-02-20', 2, ARRAY['LM-32 - Master Degree in Computer Engineering','LM-03 - Master Degree in Landscape Architecture','LM-13 - Master Degree in Pharmacy and Industrial Pharmacy']::text[]),
('Comportamento dinamico di "lattice structures" da manifattura additiva: modellazione e validazione sperimentale', 179, 'depasquale.giorgio@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY['ADDITIVE MANUFACTURING','DINAMICA','LIGHTWEIGHT','MECCANICA STRUTTURALE','MODELLAZIONE A ELEMENTI FINITI','STRUTTURE TRABECOLARI']::text[], 'TEORICA/SPERIMENTALE', ARRAY['29- Smart Structures And Systems']::text[], 'Le strutture trabecolari sono oggetto di studio per la realizzazione di componenti ad elevato rapporto resistenza/peso.
