('Human activity recognition in Parkinson''s disease using wearable sensors and artificial intelligence', 370, 'borzi.luigi@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['olmo.gabriella@tmtest.polito.it']::text[], ARRAY['MACHINE LEARNING','PARKINSON''S DISEASE','PATTERN RECOGNITION','SIGNAL PROCESSING','WEARABLE DEVICES']::text[], 'EXPERIMENTAL APPLIED', ARRAY['System Biology Group - Sysbio']::text[], 'The thesis focuses on the labelling and analysis of a large dataset of inertial signals collected from people with Parkinson''s disease.
