- by when you aim to graduate and an estimate of the time you can devote to the thesis in a typical week', '2023-11-30', 2, ARRAY['LM-10 - Master Degree in Conservation of Architectural and Environmental Heritage','LM-17 - Master Degree in Physics','LM-06 - Master Degree in Biology']::text[]),
