('Circular cities and society', 438, 'lombardi.patrizia@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['torabimoghadam.sara@tmtest.polito.it','Chiara Genta']::text[], ARRAY['CIRCULAR ECONOMY','URBAN PRACTICES','SYSTEM DYNAMICS']::text[], 'THESIS ABROAD', ARRAY['L-42 group 1']::text[], 'The proposed research aims at exploring how citizens and urban actors can contribute to the implementation of circular economy principles in cities. The thesis will focus on the analysis of existing case studies, the implementation of participative design-thinking methodologies to engage stakeholders in the design of a transformative scenario for a circular city, and the assessment and prioritization of the proposed scenarios.', ARRAY[]::text[], '', '2025-09-15', 1, ARRAY['L-42 - History']::text[]),
