('Android Auto/Apple CarPlay: onboard payment solution', 99, 'patti.edoardo@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['Davide Tonella (D.Tonella@Reply.It)']::text[], ARRAY['ANDROID','APPLE CARPLAY','AUTOMOTIVE','SMART VEHICLES']::text[], 'SPERIMENTALE', ARRAY['Dauin - Gr-06 - Electronic Design Automation - Eda','Electronic Design Automation - Eda','Gr-06 - Electronic Design Automation - Eda','Ict4Ss - Ict For Smart Societies']::text[], 'Recently, both Android Auto and CarPlay have implemented the possibility to perform payments directly from within the vehicle. Hence, the scope of the thesis is to explore this new added capability and develop a solution for payment to be compatible with either or both platforms.
