Paolo Marocco (Denerg)']::text[], ARRAY[' connected areas for RES and connected end-users)']::text[], 'Tesi di Laurea', ARRAY['Steps-Denerg']::text[], 'Supervisors: 
-	DIMEAS (G. Bracco, A. Ghigo, R. Novo)
