('Development of pH-Sensitive Hydrogel Nanoparticles as Analytical Probes for Real-Time pH Monitoring in Pharmaceutical Manufacturing and Formulation Design', 138, 'pisano.roberto@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY['HYDROGEL','NANOPARTICLES','PH SHIFT','PHARMACEUTICAL FORMULATION','PHARMACEUTICAL MANUFACTURING']::text[], 'EXPERIMENTAL', ARRAY['L-38 group 1']::text[], 'This master''s thesis will focus on the synthesis and application of hydrogel nanoparticles with pH-sensitive properties to serve as advanced analytical tools for monitoring pH changes during various stages of pharmaceutical manufacturing processes. The research will explore the potential of these nanoparticles to guide drug product formulation design and optimize manufacturing conditions.', ARRAY[]::text[], '', '2024-09-08', 1, ARRAY['L-38 - Zootechnical Sciences and Animal Production Technologies']::text[]),
