(' Control and non-linear energy dissipation devices in pipeline systems for chemical plants', 102, 'ceravolo.rosario@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['matta.emiliano@tmtest.polito.it','Luca Zanotti Fragonara (Lecturer At Cranfield University Uk','Eed Lab)','Mahesh Murugan Jaya (Eed Lab','R3C)']::text[], ARRAY['EARTHQUAKE ENGINEERING']::text[], 'EXPERIMENTAL AND SIMULATIONS', ARRAY['Centre Of Autonomous And Cyber-Physical Systems','Cranfield University','Uk','Earthquake Engineering & Dynamics Lab','Marie Sk³Odowska-Curie Itn Xp-Resilience Team','Responsible Risk Resilience Interdepartmental Centre (R3C) Www.R3C.Polito.It']::text[], 'No description available', ARRAY[]::text[], '', '2024-10-30', 2, ARRAY['LM-03 - Master Degree in Landscape Architecture','LM-10 - Master Degree in Conservation of Architectural and Environmental Heritage','LM-09 - Master Degree in Medical, Veterinary, and Pharmaceutical Biotechnology']::text[]),
