('Improving validation of Instadose dosimeters using machine learning algorithms', 172, 'testoni.raffaella@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY['Federica Roberto (Sck-Cen)','Filip Vanhvere (Sck-Cen)']::text[], ARRAY[' achieve a high level']::text[], 'Tesi di Laurea', ARRAY['L-01 group 2']::text[], 'The goal of the project is to develop a tool in order to help the validation of the dose results, by means of Machine Learning methods, achieve a high level of accuracy in identifying dosimeter results warranting expert attention, thereby minimizing the manual effort required for result validation.', ARRAY[]::text[], '', '2024-06-28', 1, ARRAY['L-01 - Cultural Heritage']::text[]),
