('Computazione in-RAM e GTM: sviluppo di un processore basato sulla computational-RAM per l''autonomous driving', 452, 'sterpone.luca@tmtest.polito.it', ARRAY[]::text[], ARRAY['AUTONOMOUS GUIDED VEHICLES','PROCESSORI']::text[], 'Tesi di Laurea', ARRAY['Dauin - Aerospace And Safety Computing Lab']::text[], 'Today, autonomous driving applications require an efficient and reliable computational power in order to achieve completely self-driving car on a robotic vehicle. The main goal of the present thesis is the development of a processing core for image elaboration and based on the computational RAM technique. The thesis is done in cooperation with Punch Softronix.', ARRAY[]::text[], '', '2024-01-26', 2, ARRAY['LM-25 - Master Degree in Automation Engineering','LM-25 - Master Degree in Automation Engineering','LM-02 - Master Degree in Archaeology']::text[]),
